graph.layout

Class Layouter<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.layout.Layouter<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The vertex type
    E - The edge type

    public class Layouter<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Layouter accepts lists of veritces and edges which might in fact form more than one graph It then forms the graphs which can later be layouted using the desired method
    Author:
    Renata
